---
import Icon from 'astro-icon'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import Splitter from '../assets/img/splitter.svg'
---

<div class="windows-comparison">
    <div class="heading">
        <h2>
            <span class="highlight">Atlas</span> vs. <span class="darken"> Windows</span>
        </h2>
        <p>With reduced processes, lower RAM usage, and improved in-game framerates, why wouldn't you consider making the switch?</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cards hide">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <Icon name="cpu-icon" class="icon" height="28px" alt="processes cpu icon" />
                    <h3>Processes</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Atlas strips out a bunch, significantly reducing Windows' bloated process count from 145 to just 35.</p>
                <span>145 -> 35~</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <Image src={Splitter} alt="Section splitter" />
        <div class="card">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <Icon name="bolt-icon" class="icon" height="32px" alt="bolt memory icon" />
                    <h3>Ram usage</h3>
                </div>
                <p>Thanks to Atlas we've freed up 1.4GB of RAM usage from boot, which can then be allocated to other tasks.</p>
                <span>2.3GB -> 900MB~</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <Image src={Splitter} alt="Section splitter" />
        <div class="card">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <Icon name="rocket-icon" class="icon" height="28px" alt="rocket fps icon" />
                    <h3>1% FPS</h3>
                </div>
                <p>We saw a significant improvement in FPS lows. With an increase from 289 on Windows to 394 FPS with Atlas.</p>
                <span>289 FPS -> 394 FPS</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- <div class="benchmark-link">
                <a href="/">View detailed benchmarks -></a>
            </div> -->
</div>

<style lang="scss">
    .windows-comparison {
        margin-top: 300px;
        margin-bottom: 300px;

        .benchmark-link {
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline;
            display: flex;
            margin: 65px auto;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;

            a {
                color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            }
        }

        .heading {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;

            p {
                max-width: 544px;
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 60px;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            span {
                font-weight: 600;
            }
        }

        .cards {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 75px;
            background-color: var(--bg-card-color);
            border-radius: 5px;
            align-items: center;

            .splitter {
                width: 2px;
                height: 300px;
            }

            .card {
                display: flex;
                width: 33.3%;
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 70px 60px;

                .content-wrapper {
                    display: flex;
                    gap: 35px;
                    flex-direction: column;
                    animation: fadeup ease-out;
                    animation-timeline: view();
                    animation-range: entry -80% exit -200%;
                    align-items: center;
                    justify-content: center;
                    text-align: center;

                    .card-title {
                        display: flex;
                        align-items: center;
                        gap: 20px;

                        .icon {
                            stroke: var(--icon-white);
                            fill: transparent;
                        }

                        img {
                            width: 28px;
                            height: 28px;
                        }

                        h3 {
                            font-size: 36px;
                            font-weight: 600;
                        }
                    }
                }

                span {
                    color: rgba(26, 145, 255, 1);
                    font-weight: 600;
                    font-size: 20px;
                }
            }
        }
    }
</style>
